DokuWiki / Mantis integration
=============================

This is the source code for the DokuWiki authentication back-end, allowing to
use MantisBT to automatically login to DokuWiki (single sign-on).

The integration was originally documented in the
[MantisBT Wiki](https://mantisbt.org/wiki/doku.php/mantisbt:issue:7075:integration_with_dokuwiki)
and related pages.
